values: Wow its been exactly a month since my last update. Thats so lazy. Well I stayed home sick all day which was terrible but by the end of the week i will have over 300 dollars to go shopping so thats gonna be great. Saras out of town at running camp and thats awful. Its so quiet at my house without her. haha. Well at least my dad found me a car. its a volvo and a big fixer upper but at least its a car. I just hope it will be done in time for school.
feeling a little bit better since the last time i wrote in this. goin surfing friday that should be fun!!
today was a terrible day and so was sunday. definitley need some cheering up!!!

Well I'm so sore right now but yesterday was my great Cassandra, Gentry, Jono and I all went surfing and out to eat. Cassandra and I were alittle late picking up the boys (just an hour) but we got there at 8am so we were good. A dolphin came like 2 feet away from me and Cassandra it was so cool! We stayed out there for maybe 4 to 5 hours. It was freezing! We got dressed (quickly lol) and went downtown to the Mellow Mushroom to eat so good food! After that we headed home and i went to help Elena get ready for prom then i went out to a movie with selimah and out to ice cream! it was a very busy day but so so so much fun.

wow i haven't written in this since saturday... well sunday we had church. jono and i went to take pics of the old church for my art project. they look so good. Then we all had practice for youth sunday. I'm reading in 2 services and kinda nervous. Monday was really slow moving. it was boring. after school though i went to the timrod library and studied for about 2 hours until they closed then i went for a walk to the toy store and bought some candy. i did the same thing tuesday it was great lol. wow i never get and comments on this :( that stinks. well almost time for church.

Well today i woke up fairly late but its the weekend so thats ok. I called cassandra to see what she was up too. Jono called about his game so mrs. poelker came and picked me up and we went to west ashley high school to watch the game. it was a good game. really close but we had a good goalie. after that mrs poelker, dustin, jono, and i went to barns and noble to look at some books and get some coffee but i dont like coffee so i got some hot chocolate and a cookie. then i went home and then to the davenports to babysit. but now im home and had nothing better to do then to write in this so here i am but i think thats my whole day and church is in the morning so i better go to bed.

Well i didnt write yesterday but i was out all night with the family for my moms birthday and babysitting the kenedy kids. little lizzy took my cell and called a bunch of people. it was oh so cute. Today at school kinda sucked, but i really dont wanna talk about it. this whole year has been bad so far. i hope everything going on in my life gets better soon!

today was fun! After school i went to my best friend cassandra's house to hang out with her and her wonderful cousins who are now in town. They are so fun and sweet. I love them all!!! After listening to some great music we went to church and we got to sing one of the bestest songs ever... prince of peace!! it was great. My birthday is in 11 more days. im so so so excited. Im not gonna get the real big party i really wanted with all my friends tho but me gentry cassandra and jono are all goin surfin so that should be fun :)... i hope. wow i dont know what else to say so im just gonna go now.

Wow... i was really bored and wanted to do something so i got one of these live journal things. i hope this is a good thing but i really suck at spelling and sentence structure and what not! :) so if i mess something up you have to forgive me. i wonder if anyone will even read this. well if you do leave a comment to tell me cause if im just talking to myself im gonna delete this. lol. well church is tomorrow. that should be super fun! i always love church. Today at school was ok. we had hsap testing and it was so easy. 2 girls are sitting with us at lunch and the annoy the heck out of me and everyone else. thats no fun. im so bored right now though and im ready to hang out with cassandra this weekend. MY BIRTHDAY IS IN 12 MORE DAYS... IM SO EXCITED!
